(### File: `media_controller/pending_store.py`) Tj
T*
(Purpose:) Tj
T*
(- Manage pending-delete queue for files that cannot be deleted immediately.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Why needed:) Tj
T*
(- During playback, delete operations can fail due to file lock.) Tj
T*
(- Failed deletes are queued and retried safely.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Functions:) Tj
T*
(- `norm_path\(path\)`) Tj
T*
