T*
(  - Reads `pending_delete.json`.) Tj
T*
(  - Returns a set of pending file paths.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `save_pending\(pending\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Atomically writes pending set to JSON using temp file + `os.replace`.) Tj
