(### File: `media_controller/process_manager.py`) Tj
T*
(Purpose:) Tj
T*
(- Handle slideshow process lifecycle and PID tracking.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Functions:) Tj
T*
(- `write_pid\(pid\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Stores slideshow PID in `slideshow.pid` atomically.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `read_pid\(\)`) Tj
T*
