T*
() Tj
T*
(- `pid_exists\(pid\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Cross-platform check if process exists.) Tj
T*
(  - Windows: uses `tasklist`.) Tj
T*
(  - POSIX: uses `os.kill\(pid, 0\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `kill_pid\(pid\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Terminates process.) Tj
T*
(  - Windows: `taskkill /F /T`.) Tj
T*
(  - POSIX: tries process-group kill \(`SIGTERM` then `SIGKILL`\), fallback single PID.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `is_running\(local_process=None\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Returns running status from in-memory process or PID file.) Tj
T*
