(### File: `media_controller/web.py`) Tj
T*
(Purpose:) Tj
T*
(- Main Flask app, routes, upload/delete/config APIs, slideshow process control.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Main functions:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `_slideshow_env\(\)`) Tj
T*
(  - Creates environment for slideshow process.) Tj
T*
