T*
() Tj
T*
(  Routes inside `create_app\(\)`:) Tj
T*
(  - `index\(\)` -> `GET /`) Tj
T*
(    - Loads photo/video filenames and app status.) Tj
T*
(    - Renders `templates/index.html`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  - `start_slideshow\(\)` -> `POST /start`) Tj
T*
(    - Prevents duplicate start if PID already active.) Tj
T*
(    - Launches `slideshow.py` process.) Tj
T*
(    - Logs stdout/stderr to `slideshow.out.log` and `slideshow.err.log`.) Tj
T*
(    - Stores PID and clears stale PID on instant crash.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  - `stop_slideshow\(\)` -> `POST /stop`) Tj
T*
(    - Stops in-memory slideshow process if running.) Tj
T*
(    - Stops PID file process if exists.) Tj
T*
(    - Clears PID file.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  - `upload_file\(\)` -> `POST /upload`) Tj
T*
(    - Accepts one file from form.) Tj
T*
(    - Validates extension and routes to `photos/` or `videos/`.) Tj
T*
(    - Saves file and clears pending-delete marker for that path.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  - `set_interval\(\)` -> `POST /set_interval`) Tj
T*
(    - Reads interval from form.) Tj
T*
(    - Validates minimum `1`.) Tj
T*
(    - Saves config.) Tj
T*
() Tj
