() Tj
T*
(## 7\) Operational Notes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- For phone access, open `http://<device-ip>:5000`.) Tj
T*
(- If running inside VM:) Tj
T*
(  - Use Bridged mode.) Tj
T*
(  - NAT IP \(example `10.0.2.x`\) may not be reachable from phone.) Tj
T*
(- Some Raspberry Pi hardware may show small transition delay between media types.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 8\) Quick Maintenance Commands) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo systemctl status media-controller.service) Tj
T*
(sudo systemctl restart media-controller.service) Tj
T*
(sudo systemctl stop media-controller.service) Tj
T*
(sudo journalctl -u media-controller.service -n 100 --no-pager) Tj
